title: Episode 9: The LSE and USA
itunes:author: Mick Cox, Marcia Balisciano, Gavin Baird, Peter Trubowitz
description: Contributor(s): Mick Cox, Marcia Balisciano, Gavin Baird, Peter Trubowitz | The LSE and United States have a long, intertwined history, and in this episode, we dive into the special relationship between Americans, London, and the LSE.
